---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About" 
  description="We believe the future isn't something that happens to usâ€”it's something we create together."
>
  <section class="container py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-12 gradient-meridian bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Hi, We're Project Meridian
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-headings:text-meridian-burgundy max-w-none">
        <p class="text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed text-meridian-steel mb-8">
          We're a group of curious humans who believe the best work happens when 
          creativity meets purpose. And honestly? We're having a lot of fun figuring out what's next.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-meridian-light-gray p-8 rounded-lg my-12">
          <p class="text-xl font-medium text-meridian-dark mb-0">
            "Great things happen when people feel empowered to bring their whole selves to work. 
            We're here to help make that the norm, not the exception."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">What We're All About</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          We're partners in possibility. We don't just hand over a deck and wish you luckâ€”
          we're right there with you, building, learning, and celebrating the wins (and learning from the oops moments too).
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Our sweet spot? Helping teams and organizations unlock their potential. Whether that's 
          reimagining how you work, designing better experiences, or just figuring out what "better" even means for you.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">How We Roll</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-meridian-burgundy pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">People First, Always</h3>
            <p>Behind every process, product, and platform are real humans with real needs. 
            We start there and work outward. It's amazing what happens when you actually listen.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-meridian-burgundy pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Stay Curious</h3>
            <p>"What if we tried..." is our favorite way to start a sentence. 
            The best solutions often come from the questions nobody thought to ask.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-meridian-burgundy pl-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Learn Out Loud</h3>
            <p>We share what works, what doesn't, and what surprised us along the way. 
            Because when we all learn together, we all grow faster.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Come On In</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
          This blog? It's our digital coffee shop. A place where ideas percolate, 
          conversations spark, and "what ifs" turn into "let's try its."
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          Whether you're here to get inspired, share your own insights, or just see 
          what we're up toâ€”we're glad you're here. Pull up a chair, the conversation's just getting good.
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-meridian-burgundy text-white p-8 rounded-lg my-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Let's Connect</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4">
            The best part of what we do? Meeting amazing people doing amazing things. 
            If that's you (spoiler: it probably is), we'd love to chat.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}contact`} class="btn bg-white text-meridian-burgundy hover:bg-meridian-light-gray">
              Drop Us a Line
            </a>
            <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}rss.xml`} class="btn border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-meridian-burgundy">
              Stay in the Loop
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <p class="text-xl font-light text-meridian-steel">
            Ready to turn those "someday" ideas into "let's do this" projects?
          </p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold mt-4 text-meridian-burgundy">
            We're here for it. ðŸš€
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>